    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m putting my absolute pride and joy up for sale, and let me tell you, she is a total dream. I\u2019ve spent countless Saturday mornings hand-polishing every inch, and it really shows\u2014she still has that incredible showroom shine and that 'new car' feel every time you hop inside. Aside from a tiny, barely-there mark that you\u2019d need a magnifying glass to find, she\u2019s practically perfect. I\u2019ve cherished every mile, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as loved. Come by for a coffee and a look; I promise you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
