      "description": "Offering a truly turn-key specimen for the serious collector. This vehicle boasts a flawlessly calibrated powertrain where the valvetrain harmonics remain whisper-quiet, indicative of meticulous oil-film thickness maintenance. We\u2019ve verified the compression ratios across all cylinders to ensure peak volumetric efficiency, paired with an optimized ECU map for a perfectly linear torque curve. The suspension geometry has been precision-aligned, utilizing fresh bushings to maintain zero-deflection under high lateral loads. Every fluid circuit has been purged and filled with high-temp synthetics for superior thermal management. From the pristine undercarriage to the factory-spec chassis rigidity, this is a mechanical masterpiece that defies its age. No leaks, no lash, just pure engineering excellence.",
